   provides the basic functionalities and operations giving access to the
   functionalities for knowledge exchange in virtual communities, and
   personal agents onAndroid exploit these artifacts to execute their tasks
   while achieving their individual and collective goals. We have employed
   SMVCMS in the context of Smart Cities and found that the system fulfills
