   techniques to assess qualities such as costs, revenues, risks, and
   profitability have been previously proposed. However, they do not allow
   the modeler to properly manage uncertainty with respect to the design of
   the considered business collaboration. In many real collaboration
   projects today, uncertainty regarding the business' present or future
