   compact/dispersion city scenarios for the year 2050 are created using
   the model. Thirdly, intra-day dynamics (hourly) of electricity demand
   and supply from PVs, which is assumed to be installed to the roofs of
   all detached houses in the study area, under two urban scenarios is
   simulated. The obtained results suggest that {[}1] ``compact{''} urban
