   work on all the mobile devices is still a challenge to solve due to
   large heterogeneity among mobile devices and network. Most of mobile
   systems are built for smartphones, which constitute of only small
   percentage of all mobile devices, rest of devices are feature phones,
   which have limited capability in terms of computation or communication.
